OL,3,CBen Whittaker: The showman on ADHD,
OL,4,Cdiscipline and life beyond boxing
OL,6,FBen Whittaker has told ITV News he
OL,7,Fwants to become British boxing's next
OL,8,Fgreat showman as he prepares to return
OL,9,Fto the ring this weekend.
OL,11,FKnown for his flamboyance in the ring,
OL,12,Fthe 28-year-old heavyweight from the
OL,13,FBlack Country has built up a huge
OL,14,Fonline following.
OL,16,FWhittaker, who grew up in Darlaston,
OL,17,Fnow believes he's ready to take his
OL,18,Fprofile to the next level after
OL,19,Fsigning a long-term partnership with
OL,20,FEddie Hearn's Matchroom Boxing.
