OL,3,CBen Whittaker: The showman on ADHD,
OL,4,Cdiscipline and life beyond boxing
OL,6,FHe faces Benjamin Gavazi on Saturday
OL,7,Fin what will be his first outing under
OL,8,Fthe new deal, after signing a long-
OL,9,Fterm partnership with Eddie Hearn's
OL,10,FMatchroom Boxing.
OL,12,FSpeaking to ITV News Central Sports
OL,13,FCorrespondent Dan Salisbury-Jones,
OL,14,FWhittaker said he embraces being an
OL,15,Fentertainer as much as being a fighter.
OL,17,FWhittaker said: "Of course, I think
OL,18,Fit's part of the job. People are
OL,19,Fpaying their hard earned money.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
