OL,3,CBen Whittaker: The showman on ADHD,
OL,4,Cdiscipline and life beyond boxing
OL,6,F"They're coming out to see a show, so
OL,7,Fwhy not put on a show. For me that's
OL,8,Fwhat gets me out of bed. You know, of
OL,9,Fcourse you've got to train hard.
OL,11,F"Of course, you've got to think about
OL,12,Fthe opponent. But for me, I just think
OL,13,Fabout the kit and the ring walk".
OL,15,FHis last fight was a technical
OL,16,Fknockout against Liam Cameron. But
OL,17,FWhittaker said he hopes his new deal
OL,18,Fmeans more fights - and more
OL,19,Fcomparisons with some of boxing's best.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
