OL,3,CBen Whittaker: The showman on ADHD,
OL,4,Cdiscipline and life beyond boxing
OL,6,FHe said: "Other than Anthony Joshua
OL,7,Fand Conor Benn, I'm probably the next
OL,8,Fstar from Britain. Which is kinda
OL,9,Fcrazy to say - I'm just a kid from
OL,10,FDarleston.
OL,12,F"But it can happen to anybody. Put it
OL,13,Fdown on the table, it's going to be a
OL,14,Fbusy year next year, hopefully
OL,15,Ffighting in America as well. And with
OL,16,Fthe platform we're on we can go global
OL,17,Fso that's what I want to do."
OL,19,FWhittaker's confidence in the ring has
OL,20,Fsometimes masked how tough the
OL,21,Fpressure can be.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
