OL,3,CBen Whittaker: The showman on ADHD,
OL,4,Cdiscipline and life beyond boxing
OL,6,FAfter his last win, he gave a tearful
OL,7,Fpress conference that surprised many
OL,8,Fin the sport. But he opened up about
OL,9,Fhis mental health and how tough it can
OL,10,Fbe in the spotlight.
OL,12,FHe said: "A lot of people only see me
OL,13,Ffor about 15, 20 minutes. They only
OL,14,Fget to see me in the ring.
OL,16,F"And when I'm in the ring, I've got
OL,17,Fthat alter ego. You've got a certain
OL,18,Flook about you, you're having fun
OL,19,Fshowboating, but I'm just a normal
OL,20,Fhuman being.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
