OL,3,CBen Whittaker: The showman on ADHD,
OL,4,Cdiscipline and life beyond boxing
OL,6,F"It does get to people sometimes, and
OL,7,Fin that moment, it got to me".
OL,9,FHe said that people often misjudge
OL,10,Fhim, before adding: "A lot of people
OL,11,Fget my character wrong. I was born
OL,12,Fwith ADHD, so sometimes I go through a
OL,13,Flot of mood swings. I'm up, down,
OL,14,Fhere, there, everywhere. But a lot of
OL,15,Fpeople say I'm arrogant, I'm this, I'm
OL,16,Fthat.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
