OL,3,CBen Whittaker: The showman on ADHD,
OL,4,Cdiscipline and life beyond boxing
OL,6,F"Of course, there's sometimes racial
OL,7,Fthings. It's all good to say that
OL,8,Fbehind a phone but you don't know what
OL,9,Fthe person is going through. You see
OL,10,Fit a lot. We need men to start
OL,11,Fspeaking out about it. Maybe me crying
OL,12,Fon there helped somebody out. So I
OL,13,Fdon't mind shedding a tear now and
OL,14,Fthen."
OL,16,FWhittaker said the pressure of long
OL,17,Ftraining camps, weeks away from
OL,18,Ffamily, and the weight of expectation
OL,19,Fall fed into his emotions that night.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/8
